TRAVEL SEOUL HAIKU - THE HAN RIVER
Hangang River
....the tears, the joys
and the excitements
in the Hangang River
ripples of joys, tears
and excitements
The Han or Hangang River divides Seoul into the residential and  commercial areas.  It flows from east of the country to the West into the Yellow Sea.The South of the river makes up the commercial area of Seoul while the North, the residential area. One could imagine the joys, the excitements as Koreans drive to work each day crossing the 27 bridges linking the North and South parts of Seoul.

